# Crypto Currency Chart and Converter

Test VueJS fetch Bitcoin exchange rates

Features
1. Fetch using axios
2. Rendering using VueJS life cycle
3. Basic styling using Bootstrap
4. Tab formatting for charts and converter
5. timestamp for chart api call ( there should a stamp for any data fetched from the api for debug reasons)
6. used computed for various interactions

Possible improvements
1. Implement complete vueJS application instead of using scripts
2. Implement NPM as package manager
3. Implement VueJS components
4. Implement design patterns
5. Use Vue emits or state management (vuex)
6. Implement complex styling by components
7. Implement buy and sell converter using frombtc route on api
8. Implement prettier and eslint
9. cache request results to reduce number of api calls

